Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不直接說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像很缺鈣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為是誰的錯啊
