Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件視界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無法在空間中移動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有時間永遠伸展著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一秒會成為我的永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的盡頭在逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對 是在不停伸展
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？ 宇宙嗎？ 我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能回首
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠並不是無限
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算時間向著永遠伸展
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也終有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一秒後何時才會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向前方 到達那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能回首
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是簡訊魔嗎
