Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是「Ka Korime L Okuuru」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是如今已經失傳的古代蘇米爾語裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你已經吃過早飯了嗎」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:00.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟嚕～早安啊岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在進行{\1c&H0000FF&}時間機器{\1c&HFFFFFF&}的實驗之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓真由理熱一下炸雞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:08.25,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部 關於{\1c&H0000FF&}時間機器{\1c&HFFFFFF&}我想到了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 大事不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8號機的資訊洩露給第三者了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 我會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.10,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼狀況？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:23.16,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據情況 不惜封口我也會阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們全體都被華麗地無視？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟無論如何都不能讓機關知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通話中不要給人發簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.02,tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-36\fs43\bord0\1c&HD9DCE0&\an1\pos(650,259)}難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.02,tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-36.5\fs43\bord0\1c&HD9DCE0&\an1\pos(406,223)}難道說是FB？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F…B？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此我就都說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你知道了秘密也就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:21:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始 你就是LabMem No.005了！


